              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-8">
              <div class="flex gap-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 border border-white/10">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-400">
                    <Fragment set:html={icons.mapPin} />
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Conoscenza del Territorio</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Comprendiamo le dinamiche del mercato locale di Carmagnola e Piemonte, creando strategie digitali mirate.
                  </p>
                </div>
